track_notes: This route goes from the small car park area near Hause Point up Lad Hows to Grasmoor. The return is via the Wainwright summits of Wandope, Whiteless Pike and Rannerdale Knots. Walk completed in March 2011.

6km UP // 8km down.

Follow the Liza Beck UP, this is a bit scary in placses where the banks have washed down.

From the summit follow the main path DOWN then branch off under Rannerdale Knotts back to the road. Sorry a 1.5km road walk at the end. 

5hrs walking + activation time.
